ows:ServiceIdentification.ows:Title: NOAA Chart Tile Service
ows:ServiceIdentification.ows:Abstract: This service provides a WMTS interface to the NOAA Chart Tiles Service. Open source credits: Tile generation software based on MX Map/Chart Compiler (https://github.com/manimaul/mxmcc); WMTS interface software provided by Tile Server PHP (https://github.com/klokantech/tileserver-php), Klokan Technologies (http://www.klokantech.com).

TileMatrixSet.ows:Abstract: the wellknown 'GoogleMapsCompatible' tile matrix set defined by OGC WMTS specification
